style.art_style: Simplified cartoon, flat 2D illustration, sticker-like, vector art
style.technique: Bold black outlines, solid color fills, no gradients, minimal to no shading, clean lines
style.color_palette: Limited, muted primary colors (off-white, dark grey/black) with occasional bright accents (red/pink for expressions or details)
style.lighting: Flat, even lighting, no discernible light source, no cast shadows

character.hair: Short, smooth fur texture implied by solid colors, no detailed fur rendering or individual strands
character.eyes: Small, solid black oval dots, no pupils or irises, simple expressive shapes
character.face: Broad, somewhat flattened snout; prominent jowls; small black nose; large, rounded, erect ears; simple mouth shapes for expression
character.accessories: None (external emotional indicators like hearts or sweat lines are separate graphic elements, not character accessories)
character.body_proportions: Chibi-like, approximately 1.5-2 head height for the entire body. The head is disproportionately large, making up roughly half of the total body height.
character.limb_proportions: Extremely short and stubby legs, thick relative to their length. Legs are approximately 1/4 to 1/5 of the total body height. No distinct joints or musculature are visible.
character.torso_shape: Short, stout, barrel-like, wider than it is tall, with a vertically compressed appearance.
character.hand_style: Simplified, rounded, blocky paws. No individual toes or claws are depicted; limbs end in smooth, rounded shapes.

composition.pose: Static or minimally dynamic standing poses, often in a side profile or slight angle
composition.angle: Eye-level or slightly low-angle perspective, direct presentation of the character
composition.background: Plain white or transparent background, no environmental elements or scenery
composition.depth_of_field: Flat, no depth of field effects, everything in sharp focus

analysis.negative_prompt: realistic proportions, detailed fur, complex shading, gradients, realistic eyes, thin limbs, elongated limbs, detailed paws, individual toes, claws, musculature, complex background, environmental details, action pose, dynamic pose, blurred background, depth of field, 3D render, photorealistic, intricate details, textures
analysis.user_custom_prompt: Toes and fingers are not expressed, No joints are expressed with black lines on the front and hind feet, No reflection of light in the eyes, No whites in the eyes
